reviewText: Must buy for all Shammi fans!!  Very entertaining... lovely songs.
Very wonderful movie.  My favorite!  Loved Saira Banu and Shammi Kapoor!
It was a very good, picture and sound was amazing I enjoyed the movie and would recomend to anyone. Customer service was also great it was beyond my expectation for a first time online shopper.
This movie JUNGLEE is Shammi Kapoor's best performance and the story is worth watching because the songs in this movie makes it more elegant. YAAAHOOO Shammi's the best!!!
Best Indian Movie ever. I saw this movie back in 1962 and I was very delighted to find the DVD to watch it again. great songs and a great story.
